6. Support parallel execution compatibility
TEST GENERATION STRATEGY: When generating tests:
1. Understand the feature
2. Identify:
   - UI flows
   - API endpoints
   - DB validations
3. Generate:
   - Happy path
   - Edge cases
   - Negative scenarios
4. Use data-driven approach when applicable
OUTPUT FORMAT: Always generate:
1. Test file
2. Page Object updates (if needed)
3. Test data
4. Comments explaining logic
